BMW Experiments With Selling Cars Online, FTD Reports

-- B y   S t e f a n   N i c o l a
-- 
2011-12-01T07:15:42Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-12-01/bmw-experiments-with-selling-cars-online-ftd-reports.html
Bayerische Motoren Werke AG  is
experimenting with selling cars on the Internet as it pursues
new sales channels,  Financial Times Deutschland  said, citing  Ian Robertson , head of sales and marketing at the German carmaker.  BMW has already tested selling cars through the Web in
 China  and is mulling mobile sales teams that would bring the car
to the potential customer for a test drive, the newspaper said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Stefan Nicola in Berlin at 
 snicola2@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Angela Cullen at   acullen8@bloomberg.net  